枚举 GameObject

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<GameObject>
element.GameObject
所有已实现的接口:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<GameObject>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum GameObject
extends java.lang.Enum<GameObject>
The enumerate class GameObject represents objects in Sokoban. All GameObject in this projects, such as WALL , are implement as an instance of this class.
从以下版本开始:
1.0
作者:
Zhengtian CHU - modified
